<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10100764>
    dc:description "Fig. 5. Locations where Stenosagola clarkei (black triangle), Stenosagola egmontensis (Black circle), Stenosagola ramsayi (black squares), Stenosagola domettensis (white circle), Stenosagola eylesi (star), and Stenosagola stewartensis (white square) have been collected in New Zealand." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10100764/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10100773>
    dc:description "Fig. 9. Locations where Stenosagola connata triangles), Stenosagola huiaensis (circles), and Stenosagola northlandensis (squares) have been collected in New Zealand." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10100773/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10100775>
    dc:description "Fig. 10. Stenosagola species. a) S. huiaensis, aedeagus, dorsal view, b) S. northlandensis, aedeagus, dorsal view, c) S. thayerae, aedeagus, dorsal view, d) S. dugdalei, aedeagus, dorsal view, e) S. tararuaensis, aedeagus, dorsal view, f) S. haunuiensis, aedeagus, dorsal view, g) S. haunuiensis, wingless male head, dorsal view. Scale bars = 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10100775/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

